170
00:15:11,679 --> 00:15:15,044
Hanya masa akan menentukannya.

171
00:15:29,957 --> 00:15:31,807
Tinggalkan kami bersendirian.

172
00:15:32,828 --> 00:15:34,213
Ya, tuanku.

173
00:15:52,855 --> 00:15:56,320
